_sText:
This is the first time I have ever made a map or have ever even used the SDK.  It took me awhile to get used to how the program works but special thanks goes to VaaMap from YouTube.  His great tutorials saved me a lot of time.

Make sure you check out the box maze, ducts and pop machines. ;-)

Known bugs:
When multiple players enter a teleporter at the same time, they will get stuck at the exit.  You can get out by crouch jumping repeatedly.  I wasn't sure how to fix this.

I hope you enjoy!
